    "That is, GPT-4's raw accuracy was not significantly higher or lower at a given Fig. 1 GPT-4's MBE Accuracy in minimally tailored vs. maximally tailored prompting conditions.",
    "Bars reflect the mean accuracy.",
    "Lines correspond to 95% bootstrapped confidence intervals temperature setting or when fed a certain prompt as opposed to another (among the two prompts used in Katz et al. (2023) and the replication here) (Table 5).",
